This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as object detection and segmentation, as well as machine learning techniques for training models to perform these tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves designing an end-to-end framework for automatic prediction, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with graphics and visualization, as it involves photo editing, which falls under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also involves light direction estimation, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
